    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I found the problem. I am sorry, it is my fault. I called grpc.waitForClientReady without checking the callback error and just closed the channel as soon as the client was ready:\n\n```\n    grpc.waitForClientReady(conn, deadline, function(err) {\n        let chan = grpc.getClientChannel(conn);\n        chan.close();\n    });\n```\n\nSome calls got through before the channel got closed. It just looked like the returned error code was the cause.\n"
